{"tid":1179632,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]搵到本2011年《Yes!》雜誌，見返當年爆紅嘅Kpop男女團同埋我老友Beast，不禁淚如雨下","createTime":"2019-05-31T08:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T22:51:14.000Z","uid":76632,"like":46,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9ccd8c45285fae4696f777153c5954c6556513f0","tid":1179632,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T08:54:07.000Z","msg":"2011年時我仲係窮苦中學生，手提電話冇得上網，屋企電腦又被阿哥家姐霸住哂，收集Idol情報嘅唯一途徑就係問中學女同學借《Yes!》睇。有次借咗返歸睇，但到今日都仲未還返俾個女同學.....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/31kKuwd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F31kKuwd.jpg&h=244cf931&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nMiss A<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZOLYoa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZOLYoa.jpg&h=49186328&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nSuper Junior<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jy6tV99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJy6tV99.jpg&h=e2a4959b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n少女時代(有Jessica)，以及我老友Beast。雖然Beast只佔呢頁嘅一小角，但佢地係我心中曾佔一大片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pqPSDr4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpqPSDr4.jpg&h=4d1752bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後當然唔少得D色情廣告，曾令無數男同學為之瘋狂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，令我諗返起8年前課室個場景，又係同今日一樣落住雨。男同學係課室午息J緊本《Yes!》性教育時<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而女同學就用課室電腦播Kpop<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n諗到呢度，我就喊了，好想放多次暑假啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。消失的下雨天，我好想再淋一遍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!"},{"pid":"26295b69a578685639e8eab8f7be756bcb7c6b70","tid":1179632,"uid":76632,"like":14,"dislike":22,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T11:08:28.000Z","msg":"心血來潮去扭Yes卡，十幾抽先扭中比較有名氣嘅子瑜<img src=\"/ass